High Grade (Gunpla)

High Grade (HG) Gunpla kits provide an excellent balance of detail, articulation, and ease of assembly at 1/144 scale. With a vast selection of Mobile Suits from across the Gundam universe, HG kits are perfect for both beginners and experienced builders. Their affordability, accessibility, and evolving engineering make them a staple for any Gunpla collection.
